title: Bug 114903: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters' dialog
OB: When opening the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values for the report parameters are not displayed.
EB: The 'Show Report Parameters' dialog should display the default values of the report parameters.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Create multiple report parameters and set default values for them. 2. Drag the report parameters to the layout. 3. Open the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog.
